<h2 id="your-personal-info">Your personal info</h2>

<p>Open file <code class="highlighter-rouge">_data/me.yml</code> and modify (you donâ€™t have to give all infos):</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">name</code>: your name, e.g. <em>Anh-Thi DINH</em>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">shor_name</code>: your short name (forename), e.g. <em>Thi</em>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">email</code>: your email, e.g. <em>dinhanhthi@gmail.com</em>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">tel</code>: your telephone number.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">avatar</code>: your avatarâ€™s url. For example, <code class="highlighter-rouge">img/avatar.png</code> means that a file called <code class="highlighter-rouge">avatar.png</code> is placed at <code class="highlighter-rouge">/img/</code> folder.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">facebook</code>: your facebook username, e.g. <em>math2it</em>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">index-intro</code>: a bref discription about you. You have put the content between <code class="highlighter-rouge">""</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">cv</code>: your Curriculum Vitae fileâ€™s url. You can place your file in folder <code class="highlighter-rouge">/files/</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">favicon</code>: the small photo standing on the left of your website in a tab of Chrome.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="index-page">Index page</h2>

<p>You can modify file <code class="highlighter-rouge">index.html</code>.</p>

<h3 id="find-me-on-check">Find me on (<a href="http://localhost:4000/simple-perso/#social">check</a>)</h3>

<p>Modify file <code class="highlighter-rouge">_data/social.yml</code>:</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">name</code>: name of the platform.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">icon</code>: an icon for this platform. You should use black &amp; white icon (with transparent background). The photo should be placed in <code class="highlighter-rouge">/img/social/</code></li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">url</code>: your profile url on this platform.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">opacity</code>: if you want the icon be lighter.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="my-learning-log-check">My learning log (<a href="http://localhost:4000/simple-perso/my-learning-log">check</a>)</h3>

<p>Modify file <code class="highlighter-rouge">pages/my-learning-log.md</code>.</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">{:.finish}</code>: for the finished tasks.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">{:.ongoing}</code>: for the ongoing tasks.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">{:.delay}</code>: for the delayed tasks.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">{:.fail}</code>: for interrupted tasks.</li>
</ul>

<p>For the badges:</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;span class="tbadge badge-orange"&gt;Orange badges&lt;/span&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;span class="tbadge badge-yellow"&gt;Yellow badges&lt;/span&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;span class="tbadge badge-green"&gt;Green badges&lt;/span&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;span class="tbadge badge-blue"&gt;Blue badges&lt;/span&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;span class="tbadge badge-gray"&gt;Gray badges&lt;/span&gt;</code>.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="recent-projects-check">Recent projects (<a href="http://localhost:4000/simple-perso/project">check</a>)</h3>

<p>Modify file <code class="highlighter-rouge">_data/project.yml</code> (all the fields should be placed inside quotation marks <code class="highlighter-rouge">""</code>). List of projects are showed in <code class="highlighter-rouge">/project</code> (file <code class="highlighter-rouge">/pages/project.md</code>) and on the index page.</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">title</code>: projectâ€™s name.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">description</code>: projectâ€™s description.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">source</code>: projectâ€™s souce codeâ€™s url.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">url</code>: projectâ€™s website.</li>
</ul>

<p>ðŸ’¡ <strong>Tip</strong>: the list of projects can be put any where with the shortcut <code class="highlighter-rouge">{% include list_project.html limit=5 %}</code> (remove <code class="highlighter-rouge">limit=5</code> if you wanna show all the projects).</p>

<h3 id="recent-read-books-check">Recent read books (<a href="http://localhost:4000/simple-perso/reading">check</a>)</h3>

<p>Modify file <code class="highlighter-rouge">_data/book.yml</code> (all the fields should be placed inside quotation marks <code class="highlighter-rouge">""</code>). List of books are showed in <code class="highlighter-rouge">/reading</code> (file <code class="highlighter-rouge">/pages/reading.md</code>) and on the index page.</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">title</code>: bookâ€™s name.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">intro</code>: bookâ€™s introduction.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">author</code>: bookâ€™s author.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">goodreads</code>: the link to your review for this book on goodreads. If you donâ€™t have any review, you can put the book url on goodreads.</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">reading</code>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">true</code> if you are reading this book. If you have already read it, donâ€™t use this field!</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">mychoice</code>: <code class="highlighter-rouge">1</code> if you really like this book!</li>
</ul>

<p>ðŸ’¡ <strong>Tip</strong>: the list of books can be put any where with the shortcut <code class="highlighter-rouge">{% include list_reading.html limit=5 %}</code> (remove <code class="highlighter-rouge">limit=5</code> if you wanna show all the books).</p>

<h3 id="blog-posts-check">Blog posts (<a href="http://localhost:4000/simple-perso/blog">check</a>)</h3>

<p>All the blog posts must be placed in folder <code class="highlighter-rouge">_posts/</code> and their name should be in the form of <code class="highlighter-rouge">2019-12-06-name-of-the-post.md</code> (You have to use <a href="https://markdown-it.github.io/">markdown</a> to write the posts). List of posts are showed in <code class="highlighter-rouge">/blog</code> (file <code class="highlighter-rouge">/pages/blog.md</code>) and on the index page.</p>

<p>At the beginning of each post, you should indicate some information</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>---

---
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>ðŸ’¡ <strong>Tip</strong>: the list of posts can be put any where with the shortcut <code class="highlighter-rouge">{% include list_post.html limit=5 %}</code> (remove <code class="highlighter-rouge">limit=5</code> if you wanna show all the posts).</p>
